                <div class="step-num">1</div>
                <h3>Evaluate Credit Quality</h3>
                <p>Check the credit rating from CRISIL, ICRA, or CARE. Stick to AAA and AA+ rated bonds for safety. Review the issuer's financials and industry outlook.</p>
              </div>
              <div class="step-card">
                <div class="step-num">2</div>
                <h3>Compare Yields</h3>
                <p>Compare yield-to-maturity (YTM) across different issuers, tenures, and ratings. Factor in tax impact — post-tax yield matters more than pre-tax coupon rate.</p>
              </div>
              <div class="step-card">
                <div class="step-num">3</div>
                <h3>Place Your Order</h3>
                <p>Buy through our platform, stock exchanges (NSE/BSE), or participate in primary issues. Ensure your demat account is active for bond settlement.</p>
              </div>
              <div class="step-card">
                <div class="step-num">4</div>
                <h3>Monitor & Reinvest</h3>
                <p>Track credit rating changes, coupon payments, and market conditions. Reinvest matured proceeds to maintain your income stream and compound returns.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
